This paper is about deep reinforcement learning algorithms and their exploration strategies. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper focuses on learning-driven exploration. The second likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper discusses intelligent exploration strategies. The third likely category is cs.RO (Robotics) as reinforcement learning is often used in robotics. The fourth likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper includes experiments on first-person shooter games. The fifth likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory) as the paper discusses exploration strategies in games.
